The '''Outer Zuma''' was an [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] region of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] which consisted of [[Fusai sector/Legends|Fusai sector]], [[Kakani sector/Legends|Kakani sector]], [[Sugai sector/Legends|Sugai sector]], and [[Ikenomin sector/Legends|Ikenomin sector]].<ref name="Gamer" />

